The paper discusses active learning as a training strategy for machine learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the practical obstacles to deploying active learning, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
